  <brief_title>Study of US-ATG-F to Prevent Chronic Graft Versus Host Disease (GVHD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 3 Study of US-ATG-F to Prevent Moderate to Severe Chronic GVHD in Adult Acute Myeloid Leukemia, Acute Lymphoid Leukemia, and Myelodysplastic Syndrome Patients After Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation From Unrelated Donors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
